commitResults.messageBody:
User could not delete their save files before so now they would be able to interact with their data with more functionality

Change button view to list view instead to integrate with delete functionality

Delete will remove the file name from the list view but the file won't actually be deleted till the user move to new page.
Therefore, the method for handling deletion of file needs to check the file names from the list view not the files in the
directory

commitResults.messageTitle: Add learn and unlearn commands for the user to teach Alice or make Alice forget about certain custom commands.
commitResults.messageBody:
Alice would now be able to respond to user with specific phrase once the user have taught Alice what to respond.
This could prove to be useful for user to teach Alice a specific phrase and to respond accordingly.

The update also comes with unlearn functionality to make Alice more intuitively usable.

Note:
- User cannot teach Alice the command that Alice already know as Alice will respond back that the vocabulary user is trying to teach is untouchable
- User cannot teach the vocabulary that Alice already knows
- User cannot unteach/make Alice unlearn a vocabulary that she does not recognize or is a default command
